OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV is vulnerable: but is
OL,4,Canyone interested in buying it?
OL,5,
OL,6,FThere are times when you need to read
OL,7,Fthe business pages and financial
OL,8,Fwebsites to understand TV.
OL,10,FITV recently announced a fresh round of
OL,11,Fsavings amid disappointing figures for
OL,12,Flinear advertising.
OL,14,FBut last week was a bleak week for
OL,15,Finvestors in the Scottish broadcaster
OL,16,Fand production company STV.
OL,18,FIt's been hit by a double whammy of
OL,19,Ffalling advertising and a drop in
OL,20,Fcommissions.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
