OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV is vulnerable: but is
OL,4,Canyone interested in buying it?
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe share price plunged by around a
OL,7,Fthird.
OL,9,FSTV is now worth less than 60
OL,10,Fmillion.
OL,12,FThink about this for a moment.
OL,14,FSTV, of course, provides the Channel 3
OL,15,Fservice in most of Scotland. It is the
OL,16,Fonly part of the C3 network which is
OL,17,Fnot owned by ITV plc.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
