OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV is vulnerable: but is
OL,4,Canyone interested in buying it?
OL,5,
OL,6,FIt's online service - the STV Player -
OL,7,Fcarries ITV 1 and much original ITV X
OL,8,Fcontent in the STV area where the range
OL,9,Fof material on ITV X itself is limited.
OL,11,FAnd the production business makes a
OL,12,Fsignificant amount of content for a
OL,13,Fwhole range of broadcasters - some of
OL,14,Fit very successful - even if STV itself
OL,15,Fnow provides little regional content on
OL,16,Fits own channel beyond Ofcom licence
OL,17,Frequirements.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
