OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV is vulnerable: but is
OL,4,Canyone interested in buying it?
OL,5,
OL,6,FYet STV Group itself must surely be
OL,7,Fundervalued on the stock market just
OL,8,Fnow. It is facing challenging market
OL,9,Fconditions but it is not a basket
OL,10,Fcase.
OL,12,FThe company is worth less than the
OL,13,Famount ITV paid for UTV 10 years ago.
OL,14,F(Remember ITV bought UTV's TV assets -
OL,15,Fnot the company itself - and the fiasco
OL,16,Fof UTV Ireland was draining the
OL,17,Fcompany.)
OL,19,FIt is easy to wonder if the time has
OL,20,Ffinally come for ITV to take over
OL,21,FSTV.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
