OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV is vulnerable: but is
OL,4,Canyone interested in buying it?
OL,5,
OL,6,FIn general, any company with an unduly
OL,7,Flow share price is vulnerable to a
OL,8,Ftakeover.
OL,10,FBut I'm not sure if ITV is even
OL,11,Finterested.
OL,13,FWould the final consolidation of the C3
OL,14,Fservice really achieve that much?
OL,16,FBeyond a few synergies (and rebranding)
OL,17,Fwould ITV get much value for its own
OL,18,Fshareholders to justify the investment?
OL,20,FSTV and ITV now have a close working
OL,21,Frelationship again.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
