OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV is vulnerable: but is
OL,4,Canyone interested in buying it?
OL,5,
OL,6,FOn the other hand, the thought that ITV
OL,7,FX would be fully available in Scotland
OL,8,Fmight appeal to the company.
OL,10,FIn general, as long as STV is
OL,11,Fundervalued by the stock market it is
OL,12,Fpotentially vulnerable - whether to an
OL,13,Fagreed bid or a hostile takeover.
OL,15,FI could imagine ITV being content to
OL,16,Flive with STV as a separate company
OL,17,Funless someone else - a rival -
OL,18,Fsuddenly shows an interest.
OL,20,FA bidding war would certainly provide
OL,21,Fsome relief for STV's shareholders.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
