OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV is vulnerable: but is
OL,4,Canyone interested in buying it?
OL,5,
OL,6,FPolitically, the possibility of
OL,7,FScottish independence in 2014 might
OL,8,Fhave deterred ITV from mounting a
OL,9,Ftakeover back then. Independence is now
OL,10,Fhighly unlikely in the foreseeable
OL,11,Ffuture.
OL,13,FSo which way will it go?
OL,15,FSTV looks like a bargain - if the share
OL,16,Fprice does not improve it looks
OL,17,Fvulnerable and any further fall may
OL,18,Fwell lead to pressure from investors.
OL,20,FThere is, however, no suggestion that
OL,21,Fthe company is not viable.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
